casebody.data:
John M. McCORMICK, Employee
v.
EXEL/DPWN HOLDINGS, INC., Employer, Self-Insured (Sedgwick CMS, Servicing Agent). No. 401P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Jan. 28, 2016. Kathleen G. Sumner, Greensboro, Attorney at Law, for McCormick, John M. Brooke A. Mulenex, Charlotte, Attorney at Law, for Exel/DPWN Holdings, Inc., et al. M. Duane Jones, Charlotte, Attorney at Law, for Exel/DPWN Holdings, Inc., et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 1st of December 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 28th of January 2016."
